desc_long								关于这款游戏							Alison’s sudden illness was a shock to everyone. Doctors do not understand what was happening to her, and what caused her illness. Family and doctors are desperate, and only faithful friend never lost hope. Faithful friendfriend. An ordinary little boy named Aiden. Aiden - it's you. You have to solve the mystery of Ellison disease. Travel between the edges of reality. Defeat the mighty Mage and save the World! In this game you expect: - intriguing storyline; - 7 locations; - more than 40 scenes; - 16 original puzzles; - map with clues; - travel between the edges of reality; - original soundtrack; - the atmosphere of magic and mystery.						
